{"comments":"Carousel Render — Pure render function for carousel state.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThe render function is pure: State -> Element.\nIt composes all the carousel sub-modules to produce the final UI.\nNo side effects, no DOM manipulation — just Element construction.\n\n## Render Structure\n\n```\n.carousel-container\n  .carousel-track\n    .carousel-slide[n]\n  .carousel-nav-arrows\n  .carousel-nav-dots\n  .carousel-nav-progress\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Carousel.State (CarouselState)\n- Carousel.Slide (SlideCollection, SlideData)\n- Carousel.Navigation (NavigationConfig)\n- Carousel.Effects (SlideEffects)\n- Hydrogen.Render.Element (Element constructors)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a carousel from state and configuration\n\nThis is the main entry point for carousel rendering.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Carousel","Render"],"CarouselConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Carousel","State"],"CarouselState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Carousel","Slide"],"SlideCollection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","Carousel","Types"],"CarouselMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}